long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Have you encountered a situation where you want to search something over youtube and ended seeing click baits which eventually triggered you to open them and you just forgot you have opened youtube for something else. So, Here is the extension focus which helps you solved the issue.

This tool helps you hide feeds/click-baits on LinkedIn, Youtube, Instagram, Facebook that you don't want to see, so you can stay focused with what you search.
